    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Before Combat</b> The sahuagin baron drinks its <i>potions of bear\u2019s endurance</i> and <i>bull\u2019s strength</i>.<br/><b>Base Statistics</b> Without <i>bear\u2019s endurance </i>and <i>bull\u2019s strength</i>, the baron\u2019s statistics are <b>hp </b>83; <b>Fort </b>+9; Melee mwk trident +15/+10 (1d8+5), claw +14 (1d4+5/19\u201320 plus 1d6 cold), bite +13 (1d6+3 plus 1d6 cold); <b>Str </b>20, <b>Con </b>17; <b>CMB </b>+14, <b>CMD </b>27"
        },
        {
            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> temperate or warm ocean"
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Powerful warriors occupy the top ranks of sahuagin society."
        }
